                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live at Hackney.</p>
               <p>Do you remember either of the prisoners, and which of them, coming to your shop at any time? - Yes; 
               <persName id="t17820703-25-person256">
                  George
                   Weston
               <interp inst="t17820703-25-person256" type="surname" value="Weston"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820703-25-person256" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820703-25-person256" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             came to my shop on the 27th of November, 1781.</p>
               <p>Did he purchase any thing of you? - Yes, a number of things, to the amount of 7 l. 12 s.</p>
               <p>What name did he come to you by? - The name of 
               <persName id="t17820703-25-person257">
                  John
                   Ward
               <interp inst="t17820703-25-person257" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
