                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Do you remember how he paid you for the goods he bought of you? - He gave me a 40 l. Bank post-bill.</p>
               <p>Look at the bill. Do you know it? - This is the bill I received of him; he wrote upon the back of it, 
               <persName id="t17820703-25-person258">
                  John
                   Ward
               <interp inst="t17820703-25-person258" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
